{"type":"weapons","title":"Boomstick","summaries":["The <b>Boomstick</b> is a <linked>pre-Hardmode</linked> <linked>gun</linked>. It can occasionally be found in <linked>Ivy Chests</linked> (22.5% chance) in the <linked>Underground Jungle</linked>, and also in <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Jungle Crates</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span> (16.67% chance). It fires a spread of <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 3-4 / <span class=\"eico i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> 3 <linked>bullets</linked> per shot, but only consumes one ammo.","The Boomstick has a stronger and less accurate pre-Hardmode upgrade, the <span class=\"eil\"><span><linked>Quad-Barrel Shotgun</linked></span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4\" title=\"Desktop, Console and Mobile versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span>, and a <linked>Hardmode</linked> upgrade, the <linked>Shotgun</linked>.","Its best <linked>modifier</linked> is <b>Unreal</b>."],"statistics":{"Uses ammo":"<linked>Bullets</linked>","Damage":"14 <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 12 <span class=\"eico s i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> <span class=\"small-bold\">(Ranged)</span>","Knockback":"5.75 <span class=\"knockback\">(Average)</span> <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> / 5.5 <span class=\"knockback\">(Average)</span> <span class=\"eico s i3 i5\" title=\"Old-gen console and 3DS versions\"><b></b><i></i></span>","Critical chance":"4%","Use time":"40 <span class=\"usetime\">(Very slow)</span> <span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><